title: Ep 32: The No Titles Episode
description:
Today's proceedings:  An Apple Review of a risqué shot, a Facebook ring shaming group, a family on a fluffy blanket, and a gender reveal gone wrong.  We also discuss some business expenses for the podcast's future!
